### OpenAPI specification
GET https://{{host}}{{api_path}}/v3/api-docs

### ORDS Healthcheck
GET https://{{host}}{{api_path}}/utility/ords/ping/steve-test-{{$guid}}
Authorization: Basic {{api_username}} {{api_password}}


