### GET DF payloads

GET https://{{host}}{{api_path}}/dfpayloads/{{noticeNo}}/steve-test-{{$guid}}
Authorization: Basic {{api_username}} {{api_password}}
Accept: application/json

### POST DF payloads
POST https://{{host}}{{api_path}}/dfpayloads/{{noticeNo}}/steve-test-{{$guid}}
Authorization: Basic {{api_username}} {{api_password}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "noticeTypeCd": "IRP",
  "payload":"{\"name\":\"John\",\"noticeType\":\"IRP\",\"car\":\"Buick\",\"age\":36}",
  "active": true,
  "processed": true
}

### PUT DF payloads
PUT https://{{host}}{{api_path}}/dfpayloads/{{noticeNo}}/steve-test-{{$guid}}
Authorization: Basic {{api_username}} {{api_password}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "noticeTypeCd": "IRP",
  "payload":"{\"name\":\"Frank\",\"noticeType\":\"IRP\",\"car\":\"Buick\",\"age\":36}",
  "active": true,
  "processed": true
}

### DELETE DF payloads
DELETE https://{{host}}{{api_path}}/dfpayloads/{{noticeNo}}/steve-test-{{$guid}}
Authorization: Basic {{api_username}} {{api_password}}
Accept: application/json


